lead_paragraph: Last year's Masters winner Jordan Spieth will be the youngest player in the room when he hosts the Champions Dinner at Augusta National on Tuesday and plans to keep his own talking to a bare minimum.

headline.print_headline: Spieth Aims to Keep Low Profile as Champions Dinner Host
